    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">#        一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##       二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###      三级级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">####     四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#####    五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">######   六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="正文"><a href="#正文" class="headerlink" title="正文"></a>正文</h2><p>正文直接输入就可以了</p><p>换行时注意，要在代码中实际空出一行，<br>直接换行的话，渲染输出的时候其实是没有换行的</p><h2 id="多行代码块"><a href="#多行代码块" class="headerlink" title="多行代码块"></a>多行代码块</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">console</span>.log(<span class="string">'这是javascript代码'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    system.out.println(<span class="string">"这是java代码"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~~ 与 ``` 是一样的，都是多行代码块</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="行内代码"><a href="#行内代码" class="headerlink" title="行内代码"></a>行内代码</h2><p>正文中的代码<code>console.log(&#39;这是`javascrpit`&#39;)</code></p><p>还有<code>console.log(&#39;这是javascrpit&#39;)</code></p><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><h3 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h3><ol><li>123</li><li>456</li><li>789</li><li>10<ol><li>123</li><li>123</li><li>123</li></ol></li></ol><h3 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h3><ul><li>123</li><li>456<ul><li>789<ul><li>000</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="加粗和倾斜"><a href="#加粗和倾斜" class="headerlink" title="加粗和倾斜"></a>加粗和倾斜</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**加粗**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*倾斜*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***倾斜和加粗**</span>*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a>脚注</h2><p>脚注的详细信息无论添加到哪里，都会显示到全篇文章的最末尾</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^1</span>]: <span class="link">这是一个简短的脚注</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^bignote</span>]: <span class="link">这是一个较长的脚注</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="删除线"><a href="#删除线" class="headerlink" title="删除线"></a>删除线</h2><p><del>此段内容将删除</del></p><h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><p><code>:</code> 是表示以什么方式对齐，默认不写以左侧对齐</p><table><thead><tr><th>标题</th><th align="center">内容</th><th align="right">备注</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>标题1</td><td align="center">内容1</td><td align="right">备注1</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="语言关键字"><a href="#语言关键字" class="headerlink" title="语言关键字"></a>语言关键字</h2><table><thead><tr><th>语言名</th><th>关键字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Bash</td><td>bash</td></tr><tr><td>CoffeeScript</td><td>coffeescript</td></tr><tr><td>C++</td><td>cpp</td></tr><tr><td>C#</td><td>cs</td></tr><tr><td>CSS</td><td>css</td></tr><tr><td>Diff</td><td>diff</td></tr><tr><td>HTTP</td><td>http</td></tr><tr><td>Ini</td><td>ini</td></tr><tr><td>Java</td><td>java</td></tr><tr><td>JavaScript</td><td>javascript</td></tr><tr><td>JSON</td><td>json</td></tr><tr><td>XML</td><td>xml</td></tr><tr><td>Makefile</td><td>makefile</td></tr><tr><td>Markdown</td><td>markdown</td></tr><tr><td>Objective-C</td><td>objectivec</td></tr><tr><td>Perl</td><td>perl</td></tr><tr><td>Python</td><td>python</td></tr><tr><td>Ruby</td><td>ruby</td></tr><tr><td>SQL</td><td>sql</td></tr><tr><td>ARM汇编</td><td>armasm</td></tr><tr><td>MIPS汇编</td><td>mipsasm</td></tr><tr><td>x86汇编</td><td>x86asm</td></tr><tr><td>Elixir</td><td>elixir</td></tr><tr><td>Elm</td><td>elm</td></tr><tr><td>Erlang</td><td>erlang</td></tr><tr><td>F#</td><td>fsharp</td></tr><tr><td>Haskell</td><td>haskell</td></tr><tr><td>GLSL</td><td>glsl</td></tr><tr><td>Clojure</td><td>clojure</td></tr><tr><td>Lisp</td><td>lisp</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a>换行</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;br&gt;或者&lt;br/&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="水平线"><a href="#水平线" class="headerlink" title="水平线"></a>水平线</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">***</span></span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">___</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><hr><hr><h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">我的主页-无备注</span>](<span class="link">https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6</span>)</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">我的主页-有备注</span>](<span class="link">https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6 "我的主页备注信息"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">我的主页-无备注</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="我的主页备注信息">我的主页-有备注</a></p><h2 id="上标-下标"><a href="#上标-下标" class="headerlink" title="上标 下标"></a>上标 下标</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">### 上标 **&lt;sup&gt;[主页地址](https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6)&lt;/sup&gt;**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 下标 **&lt;sub&gt;[主页地址](https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6)&lt;/sup&gt;**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="上标-主页地址"><a href="#上标-主页地址" class="headerlink" title="上标 主页地址"></a>上标 <strong><sup><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">主页地址</a></sup></strong></h3><h3 id="下标-主页地址"><a href="#下标-主页地址" class="headerlink" title="下标 主页地址"></a>下标 <strong><sub><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/u/84e03bc5c4a6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">主页地址</a></sup></strong></h3><h2 id="图片链接"><a href="#图片链接" class="headerlink" title="图片链接"></a>图片链接</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![](/images/trojan_1.PNG)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/trojan_1.PNG" alt=""></p>]]></content>
    
